description:
Enter the classic world of slider puzzles, with a twist. Literally! Slide tiles to put together a picture in the quickest time possible. Plus tap the tile to rotate it! 

This free version includes the Kitten level. Upgrade to the full version to get all the levels including puppies, dogs, cats, and more! If it's cute then it's here! Try and beat your old scores, and as you get better increase the difficulty level. We challenge you to beat the impossible difficulty level! 

Have fun with our brain teaser, enjoy the catchy tune, love the cute pets, and try not to cheat too much with the free help (3 goes in pause menu)!
